&lt;li&gt;Monitor and communicate daily new flows, sector developments, and key company events to senior analysts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and execute primary research, including surveys of physicians and engagement with Key Opinion Leaders, to gather proprietary insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft and contribute to comprehensive research reports, including original ideas, sector and company updates, breaking news, and initiation coverage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and sustain relationships with company management teams, industry contacts, and internal sales and trading personnel, and institutional investors as experience grows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements &amp;amp; Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
