&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in equity research or investment banking preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated passion for biotechnology and life sciences sectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong work ethic, creative problem-solving skills, and resourceful approach to research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced skill in building and maintaining financial models and forecasts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional written and verbal communication skills, with an eye for detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to excel in high-intensity, fast-paced environments with tight deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Series SIE, 63, 86 &amp;amp; 87 licensing preferred, but not required upon hiring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
